{"tid":519334,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【止蝕離場】人又冇英超冠軍又贏唔到 傳摩佬冇癮諗季尾離紅魔","createTime":"2018-01-04T08:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T03:54:10.000Z","uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"387f919d699f945f205d7db1797964fe1e7c6151","tid":519334,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:55:38.000Z","msg":"曼聯目前被曼城喺英超大幅拋離，想重溫費爵爺時代嘅美夢凍過水，有傳領隊摩連奴都有可能喺季尾辭職唔撈，皆因報道指佢從來都冇當曼市係佢頭家，家陣仲住酒店，亦成日飛返倫敦探屋企人，操練時間相對受影響，所以引起球會不滿。不過，另外有報道指摩佬唔滿意球會唔開水喉畀佢買熱刺左閘丹尼路斯，搞到佢覺得好冇癮，而且球會認為摩佬手上已經有勞基梳爾，根本唔需要出成4,000萬鎊再買左閘。"},{"pid":"ecad9fb4287a4565642f829bbd04485f39a4b19c","tid":519334,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:56:43.000Z","msg":"見搞唔惦<br />\n<br />\n咁係走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9253c471cd57450145af76e5a50b46ff99dab8","tid":519334,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cea76690ece23773320df71d88ed58b953acded","tid":519334,"uid":117187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"又9up<br />\n都未摩三季<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a4b67451b4c6625125d514500d0005c70fcbd9","tid":519334,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T22:50:40.000Z","msg":"費格遜初頭都係教得差架啦"},{"pid":"0eca5687815c4c1de9e3a792991cf0b45f90611c","tid":519334,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:54:10.000Z","msg":"等夏狗走就第三度入主轟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}